channel.title: Logo request
channel.description:
Hey,
I would like to request logo for my company ElarExpress. I would appreaciate any tries. It should be attractive for customers. Its transport/moving company, we are offering any kind of moving from one place to another/heavy object transport, piano transport and so on. If there are any one who would like to give a try then please. It's new company that I'm trying to get on a road. I'm not into graphic works myself, it's custom work but it should be connected with moving/transport and of course company name. Everything else is custom. I'm not even sure about size, not too small and not too big :)
Regards, Kakur007
